name: Five Nights at Wario's: Return of the Virus 1
name_original: Five Nights at Wario's: Return of the Virus 1
description:
-Mod of FNAW 1- 

24 years have passed since Wario's attempt at a horror house had failed when his Cafe got haunted, using the money he earned he built his second factory (the location of this game) and ran it for 3 years before going missing. 7 years have passed since Wario and the rest have gone missing and the factory was occupied by the SCP foundation. Can you Survive 6 haunting nights as D199 within the factory walls?
